#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn37.31"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn37.31:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 37 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 37 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn37.31:0.2"
msgid "3. Balavagga "
msgstr "3. Powers "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn37.31:0.3"
msgid "31. Hetusutta "
msgstr "31. Cause "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn37.31:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, mātugāmassa balāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five powers of a female. "

msgctxt "sn37.31:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "sn37.31:1.3"
msgid "Rūpabalaṃ, bhogabalaṃ, ñātibalaṃ, puttabalaṃ, sīlabalaṃ. "
msgstr "Attractiveness, wealth, relatives, children, and ethical behavior. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn37.31:1.4"
msgid "Na, bhikkhave, mātugāmo rūpabalahetu vā bhogabalahetu vā ñātibalahetu vā puttabalahetu vā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjati. "
msgstr "It is not because of the powers of attractiveness, wealth, relatives, or children that females, when their body breaks up, after death, are reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm. "

msgctxt "sn37.31:1.5"
msgid "Sīlabalahetu kho, bhikkhave, mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjati. "
msgstr "It is because of the power of ethical behavior that females, when their body breaks up, after death, are reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn37.31:1.6"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañca mātugāmassa balānī”ti. "
msgstr "These are the five powers of a female.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn37.31:1.7"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
